I think this is a great change.  However it does make it so that one cannot pick "select" when both select and poll are available (that may or may not be desired by users but it has been in the wild this way).  Instead of removing the option of selection the poll method how about if we make the default None which means "pick the best one that glance supports".  Then we can still allow a user to select the method they want.  If necessary we could validate that selection against a know list of acceptable methods, however I would be inclined to give users enough rope to hang themselves and document the only supported methods (select and poll).
